      "body" : "The suggestion that &quot;It&#39;s also possible to enable automatic JavaDoc popup on code completion in Preferences | Editor | General | Code completion (Autopopup documentation)&quot; doesn&#39;t work.   That is &quot;For explicitly invoked completion&quot;, not random hover.  The <i>real</i> fix is in the answer below: &quot;Go to File/Settings, Editor, click on General. Scroll down, then ✔ Show quick documentation on mouse move.&quot;"
