    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Alternatively you can position your cursor on the item and show JavaDoc using </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>Q</kbd></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>which is the default shortcut.</p>\n\n<p>Edit: As Methical mentioned <em>on Mac</em> the shortcut is</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>j</kbd> (<kbd>^</kbd>+<kbd>j</kbd> not <kbd>⌘</kbd>+<kbd>j</kbd>) </p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
