    "creation_date" : 1384176199,
    "answer_id" : 19907477,
    "question_id" : 11053144,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is nice feature which shows quick documentation when your mouse is over element.</p>\n\n<p><strong>IntelliJ 14</strong></p>\n\n<p>Editor / General -> Show quick documentation on mouse move</p>\n\n<p><strong>Older versions</strong></p>\n\n<p>Add the following line to idea.properties file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>auto.show.quick.doc=true\n</code></pre>\n"
