    "question_id" : 11053144,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have noticed that selecting the method name and pressing F2(Quick Documentation) dispalys it's JavaDoc. \nI am using Intellij 2016, and Eclipse Keymap</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 455032,
